      "text": "un fazzija : Gwehtihis laid irr Ahbrams tam wiſſitaugſtakam STIPRAM DEEWAM / kam peederr Semine un Deb-\nbes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fivehtihts laid irr tas wiſſitaugſtakajs STIPRAJS DEEWS / kas tawus Eenaids-\nneekus tawa Rohka nodeiwis irr/ un wiꞥſch dewe tam tohs Defmi-\ntus no wiſſahm Leetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Rehninsch no So-\ndomas fazzija us Ahbranu: Dohd man tohs Landis / un to Mantu nemm preekſch tewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams fazzija us to Rehninu no Sodomas : Es eſnu fawi Rohku pzeblis us to KUN-\nGU to wiſſitaugstaku STIP-\nRU DEEWU / kam Debbes un Semme peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja es tahdu Bawedeni/\njeb weenu Kurpes-Sikſni / jeb\n(zittu fo) nemſchu no wiſſeem /\nfas tew peederr / ka tu ne warri\nfazzht : Es eſnu Ahbramn bag-\ngatu darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ween to/ fo tee Jan-\nnekti irr apehdnschi/ un to Wihro\nDaltu / kas ar man gahjnschi/\nAhnera/ Efcola un Mamrea/ lat\ntee nemm fawu Daltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XV. Nodalla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ahbramam tohp weens Dehls/un ta Osimmuma Wairoſchana joſlita : 4. Wiꞥſch tizz fchai\nBohlifchanai / un tas tohp winnam par Tai-\nſnibu peelahgadihts : 6. Ta Semme Ka-\nnân tohp winnam arridsan zour weenu Siḥ,\nmi ſſipri apjoſlita : 7. Ir ta Egiptes Wahr-\ngoschana / un Jsglahbfchana no tahs paschas\npapreekſch fludpinata : 12.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ehzſchahm Leetahm/no-\nB tikke ta KUNG-\nWahrds us Ahbram-\nweenâParahdischana/fazzidams\nEs eſnu teiv par Preekſchturra-\nmahm Bruzznahm/ un tawa Al-\nga irr tohti leela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ahbrams\nKungs / KUNGS / fo tu mar-\ndohfi / un es eemn ta bes Behr-\nneem/ un mans Namna Usrau-\nga Dehls irr fchis Damaskeneris\nEliėſers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrams fazzija : Rau-\ngi/man ne eſti tu Osimmumu de-\nwis / un redſi mannas Saines\nBehrns buhs mans Mantneeks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un raugi / ta KUNGA\nWahrds notifke uhs winnu/ faz-\nzidans : Schis ne buhs taws\nMantneeks/ bet kas no tawahm\nMecfahm nahks / tas buhs taws\nMantas-Mehnejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch iſwedde to ahra/\nun fazzija : Lubfo jelle us Debbes/\nun ſkaiti tahs Swaigſnes/warrig-\ntu tahs ſkaitibt ? Un wiꞥſch fazzt-\nja us to: ta patt buhs taws Osim-\nmuns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch tizzeja eekſch to\nKUNGU / un tas peelahgadija\nwinnam to par Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija us winnu:\nEs eſnu tas KUNGS / kas Es\ntew iſweddis eſnu no ur to Kal-\ndeëru/ ka es terw fcho Semmi doh-\ntu eemanteht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Kungs/\nKUNGS / pee ka noprattifchu\nes/ ka es to eemantofchu?\n"
    }
  ],
